These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, reggae, ambient, d&b
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, japanese, british, french
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, weightlifting, lacrosse, snowboarding
1. the french is the fan of ambient##1
2. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
3. the indian is in an odd position##4
4. the british is not the fan of rock##6
5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is not the french##6
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left or right of the indian##3
7. the indian is somewhere between the fan of ambient and the japanese##7
8. the person who's sport is tennis is between the fan of reggae and the fan of ambient##2
9. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the fan of d&b##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | d&b      | reggae   | rock  |
| Nationality   | french    | british   | indian | japanese  |
| Sport         | snowboarding | tennis | lacrosse     | weightlifting |

