.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, milk, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: carrot, apricot, pumpkin, avocado
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, turkish, french, canadian
 1. the person eating avocado is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person eating carrot is in an odd position##4
 3. the person drinking milk is not the person eating apricot##6
 4. the person drinking lemonade is the person eating pumpkin##1
 5. the person eating carrot is the french##1
 6. the person eating pumpkin is the canadian##1
 7. the person drinking milk is on the right of the turkish##1
 8. the person eating avocado is on the left or right of the turkish##3
 9. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person eating avocado and the person drinking milk##7
10. the french is on the left or right of the person eating pumpkin##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |     3     |   4    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | fanta         | milk    | lemonade  |
| Food          | avocado     | apricot | carrot | pumpkin |
| Nationality   | argentine     | turkish     | french  | canadian |

