.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, drawing, reading
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, italian, indonesian, thai
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, ship, train, skateboard
1. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
2. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the train is on the far right##1
4. the egyptian is between the thai and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person driving the skateboard##6
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is gardening and the italian##7
7. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
8. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
9. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3     |      4      |
| Hobby         | reading | drawing  | gardening  | card-games |
| Nationality   | italian   | indonesian | egyptian | thai     |
| Transport     | skateboard    | motorbike     | ship     | train         |

