.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, trance, d&b, punk
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, french, malaysian, pakistani
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, van, subway, trike
1. the fan of d&b is on the far right##1
2. the french is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the van##1
4. the fan of trance is the person driving the van##1
5. the malaysian is the fan of punk##1
6. the egyptian is the person driving the taxi##1
7. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
8. the person driving the trike is somewhere between the fan of trance and the fan of d&b##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | trance    | disco     | punk   | d&b      |
| Nationality   | french    | egyptian | malaysian | pakistani  |
| Transport     | van | taxi  | trike    | subway |

