.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-7-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, 7up, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, classical, salsa, gospel
4 different pets are kept: lizard, ferret, hedgehog, rat
1. the person drinking almond-milk is not the fan of gospel##6
2. the fan of classical is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the fan of r&b##7
3. the owner of the ferret is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the fan of classical and the person drinking mirinda##7
5. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the rat##1
6. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
7. the owner of the hedgehog is the person drinking sprite##1
8. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |  2   |    3     |    4     |
| Beverage      | mirinda  | almond-milk | 7up | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | salsa  | classical  | r&b    |
| Pet           | rat | lizard  | ferret    | hedgehog    |

