4. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is dancing##7
5. the person who's hobby is singing is the person drinking water##1
6. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
7. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
