3. the owner of the fish is between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the rat##2
4. the fisherman is somewhere to the right of the social-worker##5
5. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
6. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
7. the social-worker is somewhere between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the roller##7
8. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
9. the entrepreneur is somewhere to the left of the owner of the fish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |      4       |
