The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: time-travel, adventure, western, documentary
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, frog, goldfish, guinea-pig
 1. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 3. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##5
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
 5. the person who's hobby is rabbiting is on the far left##1
 6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching adventure movies##5
 7. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching adventure movies and the person watching documentary movies##7
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goldfish##5
10. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |    3    |     4     |
| Hobby         | rabbiting | cooking      | collecting | sudoku |
| Movie-Genre   | western     | adventure | time-travel  | documentary       |
| Pet           | guinea-pig         | goldfish       | rabbit    | frog  |

