5. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating lime##5
6. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
7. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person watching western movies##5
8. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
9. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

