3. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
4. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the fan of dubstep##5
5. the person eating apple is on the right of the fan of disco##1
6. the person eating grapes is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
7. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is rugby##5
8. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan of hip-hop##5
9. the person who's sport is rugby is not the fan of disco##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |       3       |    4    |
| Food          | avocado | kale | apple          | grapes  |
| Music-Genre   | house    | disco      | hip-hop    | dubstep   |
| Sport         | basketball | biathlon  | rugby | water-polo |

